{"tid":452183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CIA密檔曝光：希特勒二戰後10年尚在世","createTime":"2017-10-30T02:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T11:24:34.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bc1f539fc42dcbbf126b6316c80c216becc1d018","tid":452183,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">CIA密檔曝光：希特勒二戰後10年尚在世</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20171029/s00059/e9977bedc982b35f4b97ce1bb349d849.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20171029%2Fs00059%2Fe9977bedc982b35f4b97ce1bb349d849.jpg&h=58039640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】美國《國家利益》（The National Interest）雙月刊報道，中央情報局（CIA）一份解密檔案紀錄顯示，委內瑞拉加拉加斯一名署理情報首長1955年10月3日通報上級，指代號CIMELODY-3、曾在他麾下工作的一名探員，在4日前獲他信任的友人告知，德國前納粹親衛隊成員西特羅昂（Phillip Citroen）向他密報，納粹德國領導人希特勒還活着，當時距二戰結束已10年。<br />\n<br />\n委國1955年情報附希特勒照片<br />\n<br />\n這份解密備忘錄還附上一張該友人提供的照片，當中左邊男子是西特羅昂，而右邊則相信是希特勒。希特勒1945年4月30日據報在柏林一座碉堡自殺，以免遭蘇聯紅軍俘虜。多年來陰謀論甚囂塵上，包括希特勒乘亂逃到南美洲。<br />\n<br />\n（中央社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171029/s00014/1509213609198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171029%2Fs00014%2F1509213609198&d=UtW9Xjt%2BaK%2Bs9a9qy0N3Pp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=0d2c413e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171029%2Fs00014%2F1509213609198&h=6cbeadc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171029/s00014/1509213609198</a>"},{"pid":"e1170cb2262d0890cc4ee3e5a075bb35bf45e8c7","tid":452183,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:09:20.000Z","msg":"一定 KEEP 起  DNA 再整另一個"},{"pid":"131a34bbee32c0740bb15127c4e90bc4133c3340","tid":452183,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r